text: Paulette le Raer (born 7 January 1932) is a French gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:French female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint-Malo
